@startuml
left to right direction
actor "Student" as S
actor "Discord OAuth2" as O
rectangle "Student Discord Callback API" as P1
rectangle "LinkStudentDiscordUseCase" as P2
database "sysadmin_discord_bot_credentials" as D1
database "students" as D2
database "student_discord_credentials" as D3
S --> P1 : code/state callback or cancel
P1 --> P2 : OAuth callback input
P2 --> D1 : load OAuth client credential
P2 --> D2 : verify student exists when building URL
P2 --> O : exchange code and fetch user
O --> P2 : token set + user profile
P2 --> D3 : upsert Discord identity and token
P2 --> P1 : success/cancelled status
P1 --> S : HTML postMessage + close popup
@enduml
